92992.name: Recipe: Iron Legion Staff
92992.description: A recipe to make an Iron Legion Staff.

92994.name: Reconsideration
92994.description: <c=@flavor>"Got chased in here by the biggest Branded devourer I'd ever seen. Thought I'd starve to death. Never thought I'd see a human lure it away."</c>

92995.name: Redeployment Order
92995.description: <c=@flavor>"Vishen Steelshot: immediately regroup with Steel warband at Terra Carorunda Waypoint for an important assignment."</c>

92997.name: Disappointment
92997.description: <c=@flavor>"I went renegade because they said we'd be heroes when we eradicated the humans for good, but here I am sitting in a dank cave sharpening rusty swords."</c>

92998.name: Secret of the Raven Reflector
92998.description: <c=@flavor>"Scouted a reflector overlooking a Bear shrine. Lines up with others nearby. Then spotted the tower to the southwest..."

92999.name: Dark Wing Shield Skin
92999.description: Double-click to apply this look to any other shield.

93003.name: Dark Wing Scepter Skin
93003.description: Double-click to apply this look to any other scepter.

93004.name: Echo of Whispers
93004.description: Double-click to open. Contains loot found in medium essence chests or rewarded from earning silver rank in the Whisper of Jormag Strike Mission.

93005.name: The Ebonlocke Covenant
93005.description:
<c=@flavor>Love is a battlefield.</c>
Confiscated from the Brig in Grothmar Valley.

93006.name: The Passions of Faren
93006.description:
<c=@flavor>He's rich...with a burning passion!</c>
Banned for sedition against the God King and sealed in the warehouse of Vehtendi Academy in the Domain of Vabbi.

93011.name: Journal Scrap
93011.description: <c=@flavor>"First Posting: On loan to Reave warband in Redreave Mill. Mountain makes sentry duty easy. Good sight lines. Campfire talk says there's a killer festival at Butcher's Block."</c>

93012.name: Emblem of Tournament Victory
93012.description: In the Mystic Forge, combine Slumbering Transcendence, 250 Unidentified Dyes, an Emblem of Tournament Victory, and an Essence of Llamatic Elegance to create Transcendence.

93014.name: Hoelbrak Gate Link
93014.description: Adds Hoelbrak as a destination to the Eye of the North gate.

93016.name: Salt-Forged Mist Diamond
93016.description: In the Mystic Forge, combine a Salt-Forged Mist Diamond with a Gift of the Mists, a Gift of Competitive Dedication, and 100 Icy Runestones to create Gift of the Champion.

93018.name: Love Is Blind
93018.description:
<c=@flavor>Hearts collide in the frigid tunnels of the Shiverpeaks.</c>
Found in the Grotto in Thunderhead Peaks.

93020.name: Distilled Hylek Mead
93020.description:
<c=@flavor>"Burns long, hot, and clean. Perfect for a flaming sword."
—Vash</c>

93021.name: Charred Slip of Paper
93021.description: <c=@flavor>"Tribune, the renegade that just pledged Blood in the trials would be a fine addition to Steel. Make it happen, but do not show my hand.  —B"</c>

93022.name: Emblem of Victory
93022.description: In the Mystic Forge, combine a Vial of Salt, an Emblem of Victory, a Mist Diamond, and a Mist-Enhanced Orichalcum to create a Salt-Forged Mist Diamond.

93024.name: Pristine Fang of the Whisper
93024.description:
Can be attained from the Whisper of Jormag.
Trade to Berghild in Eye of the North for boots.

93025.name: Shattered Chest Lid
93025.description: <c=@flavor>"This chest has been puzzling me for a while. I see no way to reach the mechanism through this field...unless you're a tank-mounted harpoon."</c>

93029.name: Broken Rod
93029.description:
<c=@flavor>"Our primus used to beat us with a rod to toughen us up, until one day he didn't."
—Ryland Steelcatcher</c>

93031.name: Ash Legion Combat Blade of Celerity

93032.name: Resistance
93032.description: <c=@flavor>"Some of the warband are starting to eye each other in the wrong way. Got to silence the whispers."</c>

93034.name: Mist Diamond

93036.name: Gift of the Champion
93036.description: In the Mystic Forge, combine a Gift of the Champion with a Mist Pendant, a Mystic Tribute, and a Gift of Skirmishing to create Transcendence.

93038.name: Echo of Raven Sanctum
93038.description: Double-click to open. Contains loot found in medium essence chests or rewarded from earning silver rank in the Raven Sanctum Strike Mission.

93039.name: Frayed Braid of Charr Fur
93039.description: <c=@flavor>Some charr make small braids of their lover's fur to carry with them.</c>

93045.name: Redemption
93045.description: <c=@flavor>"I now see my duty to be a good soldier, and I'll never waver again."</c>

93053.name: Recruitment Notes: Vishen Steelshot
93053.description: <c=@flavor>"Could have been a valuable asset, but too tightly bonded to warband for recruitment. Reinitiate contact if a schism with Steel is managed."</c>

93054.name: Shard of Elemental Ice
93054.description: <c=@flavor>Blood Legion cubs would dare each other to take a shard from the biggest sleeping elemental they could find.</c>

Trade to Berghild in Eye of the North for a coat.

93057.name: Blood Legionnaire Badge
93057.description: <c=@flavor>Given to young legionnaires when they graduate from the fahrar and take command of their warband.</c>

93060.name: Aspiration
93060.description: <c=@flavor>"I grew up on stories of charr heroes. I wanted to be one so badly, I'd do anything."</c>

—Crystallographer Smoxxi</c>

93076.name: Crystallographer Smoxxi's Thoughts
93076.description:
<c=@flavor>"You can't just grab a weapon and go running around touching things. Doesn't work that way. I reharmonize it, then you run around touching things."
—Crystallographer Smoxxi</c>

93078.name: Collaboration
93078.description: <c=@flavor>"I asked a Flame shaman if he would share any tonic recipes. He agreed on the condition that I performed a ritual to carry flame without a torch. Is...is this a joke?"</c>

—Ranoah</c>

93118.description: <c=@flavor>"Steel warband's vigilance in holding the pass behind Brokentooth Maw prevented the Shatter warband from being overrun."</c>

Found in the Pact base in Dragonfall.

93151.description: In the Mystic Forge, combine a Vial of Salt, an Emblem of Victory, a Mist Diamond, and a Mist-Enhanced Orichalcum to create a Salt-Forged Mist Diamond.

93152.name: Roasted Meat
93152.description: <c=@flavor>"I don't like how the smell of all this smoke lingers on my fur, but I liked spending downtime with Vishen. Was great to see her eyes light up when we grilled the meat."</c>

93153.name: Unlock Specialist Vendors

93154.name: Crystallographer Smoxxi's Thoughts

Double-click to open.
The weapons in this box unlock a journey to acquire multiple versions of their appearances.

93157.name: Green Prophet Shard
93157.description:
Crystalline shards of dragon magic, veined with green.

93158.name: Strong Echo of the Shiverpeaks
93158.description: Double-click to open. Contains loot rewarded for earning gold rank in the Shiverpeaks Pass Strike Mission.

93164.name: Assignment Request
93164.description:
<c=@flavor>"Ever since the ghost incident, Ranoah has been underfoot in the motorpool. She has aptitude but needs honing. Recommend we station her with Iron for a while."
—Quaestor Blackclaw</c>

93166.name: Lion's Arch Gate Link
93166.description: Adds Lion's Arch as a destination to the Eye of the North gate.

93167.name: Dark Wing Longbow Skin
93167.description: Double-click to apply this look to any other longbow.

93168.name: Frostbone Flux
93168.description: <c=@flavor>While acting as a standard flux purifying the metal, it also suffuses it and protects it from softening due to constant heat exposure.</c>

93169.name: Experimentation
93169.description: <c=@flavor>"Melted snow makes a great solvent for tonics, so you'd think melted eternal ice would be better. But the stuff doesn't melt! However, I can powder it and make a suspension..."</c>

93171.name: Mini Nicabar Steelweaver
93171.description: Double-click to summon this mini to follow you around. Only one mini may be in use at a time.
